{
  "stem": "10.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They didn't identify.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So we think it's not his body.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Now, even less than a month, somebody called me, a woman from Salt Lake City.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It's a habit.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "She looks after Mengele-- how he died, where he was, if he's still alive.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And she thinks this is the body of his brother.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So we don't know, but this is separate, yeah.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "In Auschwitz this went on-- yes, but I was there in the beginning a week, and I returned from the Sunday, from the football game, from the soccer game.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "My block eldest, my camp eldest isn't there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Well, I laid down.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "In the morning he's not there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I had to give the report to the SS men, the roll call.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And he comes to the camp, and I give him the report, saw so many people-- one is missing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They knew already that one is missing because [PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] the fence was cut, and he escaped.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And he could escape because this spot of the camp, on Sunday when all the people in the camp not going out to work, this was not occupied.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Only the fence was there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He knew about it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "He did say escape on Sunday.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "He went through and disappeared.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "They never caught him, and we never knew what happened to him.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But we think he made it to the Poles, in the mountains, but he was killed right away because he didn't speak Polish, only German.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They considered him as a spy and they killed him.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His name?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Rudy Kahn.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was a German-Jew and half-Jew, and no trace about him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After a while when the SS men reported that they found the missing one-- I mean, he is from the re-educational camp, the kapo, the block eldest.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
